* Program....: qf.prg
* Version....: 1.01
* Author.....: Randy Wallin
* Date.......: August 4, 1993     Last Modified: 08/04/93 @ 11:40 pm
* Notice.....: Copyright (c) 1993 COB System Designs, Inc., All Rights Reserved.
