HEADER={
* Program....: ##FILE##
* Version....: ##VERSION##
* Author.....: ##NAME##
* Date.......: ##FILEDATE##     Last Modified: ##DATE## @ ##TIME##
* Notice.....: Copyright (c) ##YEAR## ##COMPANY##, All Rights Reserved.
